description: Bin Buddy helps newcomers to San Francisco figure out how to dispose of any item. Simply ask Bin Buddy what you want to get rid of, and Bin Buddy will tell you what bin it goes in.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Bin Buddy where to put envelopes.
Alexa, ask Bin Buddy where food scraps go.
Alexa, ask Bin Buddy what bin to put aluminum cans in.
name: Bin Buddy
shortDescription: Bin Buddy helps San Francisco residents know what goes in what bin.
